## Usage

Check available version in OCI repo:
```
crane ls ghcr.io/kedify/charts/otel-add-on | grep -E '^v?[0-9]'
```

Install specific version:
```
helm upgrade -i oci://ghcr.io/kedify/charts/otel-add-on --version=v0.0.7
```

